    "summary": "The advocate emphasizes the project's potential for educational impact, scientific backing through spaced learning, and successful integration of multiple technologies despite challenges. They highlight the proactive AI approach and clear future vision. The critic points out lack of concrete metrics, technical limitations, heavy reliance on third-party services, and questions the project's novelty and differentiation from existing solutions.",

