    "final_verdict": "The Deeper Learning Coach shows promise as an educational technology concept with a solid foundation in learning science. While the solo implementation achieved a working proof-of-concept, substantial development is needed for production readiness. Recommendations: 1) Develop robust backend architecture with proper security measures, 2) Create clear differentiation strategy from existing solutions, 3) Implement concrete success metrics, 4) Reduce dependency on third-party services where possible, 5) Focus on mobile development as planned for better accessibility. Overall score: 6.25/10 - A promising concept that requires significant refinement for market viability."
